            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro pace Au<supplied reason="lost">gusti</supplied> in honorem <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> Claudi <lb n="2"/>Germanici <supplied reason="lost">Caesaris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>divi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> perpetuus sacer<lb break="no" n="4"/>dos <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <supplied reason="lost">Aquila pr</supplied><expan><abbr>aef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fabr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> bis <lb n="5"/>in <expan><abbr>aerar</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> delatus <lb n="6"/>a co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Gabin<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>o <supplied reason="lost">Secundo Ta</supplied>uro Statilio Corvino mon<lb break="no" n="7"/>tem cecidit e<supplied reason="lost">t viam <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>essionem <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ὑπὲρ τῆς Σεβα<supplied reason="lost">στῆς εἰρήνης καὶ εἰς</supplied> τὴν τειμὴν Τιβερίου Κλαυ<lb break="no" n="2"/>δίου Γερμ<supplied reason="lost">ανικ</supplied>ο<supplied reason="lost">ῦ Καίσαρος Σεβαστ</supplied>ο<supplied reason="lost">ῦ</supplied> ὁ τοῦ ἐπουρανίου Θεοῦ Σ&amp;lt;ε&amp;gt;βαστοῦ ἀρχ<supplied reason="lost">ιερεὺς διὰ βίου<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> Γάϊος</supplied> Ἀκυίλας ἔπαρχος <lb n="3"/>δὶς εἰς τὸ αἰρ<supplied reason="lost">αρίον ἀναφερόμεν</supplied>ος ὑπὸ ὑπάτων Ὤλου Γα<lb break="no" n="4"/>βεινίου Σεκού<supplied reason="lost">νδου καὶ Ταύρου Στα</supplied>τειλίου Κορουίνου τὸν λόφον <lb n="5"/>κόψας τὴν ὁδ<supplied reason="lost">ὸν <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>ον ἐκ τῶν ἰδίων ὑπαρχόντων <lb n="6"/>ἐποίησεν
            </ab></div></div>
